title: Teacher Created Resources Everyone is Welcome Pom-Poms and Tassels Garland (TCR7157)
description: Instantly brighten any space with these pom-pom and tassel garlands. These fun and festive garlands will add the perfect splash of color to your home or classroom, or use it to celebrate any special occasion. Each garland measures 60 inches in length. Pom-poms are approximately 1-1/2" in diameter. Tassels are approximately 5" in length.
